            <abstract>
                <p>This miracle occurs as a single miracle,
                    <ref type="work" corresp="LIT5248MiracleStephanites"/>, and also 
                    divided into two distinct miracles, <ref type="work" corresp="LIT5649MMStephanites1"/> and 
                    <ref type="work" corresp="LIT5650MMStephanites2"/>.
                    There are apparently several recensions of the first part of the miracle, ending either in the stoning or repentance of the heretics. This
                is the general ID to be used in cases where the recension cannot be identified.</p>
